              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Conversation Rate</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Percentage of visitors who engage</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Average Session Length</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Time spent in conversations</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Message Volume</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Total interactions over time</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="analytics-card">
            <div class="analytics-icon">üë•</div>
            <h3>User Insights</h3>
            <p>Understand your users like never before. See what questions they ask, what problems they're trying to solve, and what information they're seeking. Identify trends, common pain points, and opportunities for improvement.</p>
            <div class="metrics-list">
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Top Questions</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Most frequently asked queries</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">User Intent</span>
                <span class="metric-description">What users are trying to achieve</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Behavior Patterns</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Navigation and interaction flows</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="analytics-card">
            <div class="analytics-icon">üìã</div>
            <h3>Actionable Reports</h3>
            <p>Transform raw data into actionable insights with comprehensive reports. Export data, create custom dashboards, and integrate with your existing analytics tools to get a complete picture of your website's performance.</p>
            <div class="metrics-list">
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Custom Dashboards</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Visualize data your way</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Automated Reports</span>
                <span class="metric-description">Scheduled insights delivery</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-label">Data Export</span>
                <span class="metric-description">CSV, JSON, and API access</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Security and Reliability -->
    <section class="content-section bg-secondary">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Security and Reliability</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Enterprise-grade security and infrastructure you can trust.</p>

        <div class="security-grid">
          <div class="security-card">
            <div class="security-icon">üîí</div>
            <h3>Data Protection</h3>
            <p>Your data security is our top priority. We employ industry-leading encryption, comply with international privacy regulations, and implement strict access controls to ensure your information remains safe and private.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>End-to-end encryption</strong> for all data transmission</li>
              <li><strong>GDPR, CCPA, and SOC 2</strong> compliance</li>
              <li><strong>Regular security audits</strong> by third-party experts</li>
              <li><strong>Data anonymization</strong> and privacy protection</li>
              <li><strong>Secure data centers</strong> with 24/7 monitoring</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="security-card">
            <div class="security-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
            <h3>Robust Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>Built on world-class infrastructure with redundancy at every level. Our distributed architecture ensures your conversational interface is always available, fast, and responsive, no matter where your users are located.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>99.9% uptime guarantee</strong> with SLA backing</li>
              <li><strong>Global CDN</strong> for lightning-fast delivery</li>
              <li><strong>Automatic failover</strong> and disaster recovery</li>
              <li><strong>Load balancing</strong> for optimal performance</li>
              <li><strong>Real-time monitoring</strong> and alerting</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="security-card">
            <div class="security-icon">üìà</div>
            <h3>Scalability</h3>
            <p>From startups to enterprises, Minimal scales with your business. Our infrastructure automatically adjusts to handle traffic spikes, seasonal variations, and growth without any intervention required from you.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Auto-scaling infrastructure</strong> handles any traffic volume</li>
              <li><strong>No performance degradation</strong> during high traffic</li>
              <li><strong>Resource optimization</strong> for cost efficiency</li>
              <li><strong>Enterprise support</strong> for large-scale deployments</li>
              <li><strong>Custom solutions</strong> for specific requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- User Experience -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>User Experience</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Designed with both your users and your team in mind.</p>

        <div class="ux-grid">
          <div class="ux-card">
            <div class="ux-icon">‚ú®</div>
            <h3>Intuitive Interface</h3>
            <p>Our conversational interface is designed to feel natural and effortless. Users don't need training or instructions - they just start typing and get immediate, helpful responses. The clean, modern design ensures the focus stays on the conversation.</p>
            <div class="ux-features">
              <span class="ux-tag">Natural language input</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Smart suggestions</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Quick replies</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Rich media support</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Mobile-optimized</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Accessibility compliant</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ux-card">
            <div class="ux-icon">üé®</div>
            <h3>Visual Customization</h3>
            <p>Make Minimal truly yours with extensive customization options. Match your brand perfectly by adjusting colors, fonts, spacing, position, and behavior. All changes can be made through our intuitive dashboard - no coding required.</p>
            <div class="ux-features">
              <span class="ux-tag">Custom colors</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Brand fonts</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Logo integration</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Position control</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Theme modes</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Animation settings</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ux-card">
            <div class="ux-icon">üöÄ</div>
            <h3>Advanced Features</h3>
            <p>Power users and developers can take advantage of advanced features including JavaScript API, webhooks, custom actions, and programmatic control. Build sophisticated workflows and integrate deeply with your existing systems.</p>
            <div class="ux-features">
              <span class="ux-tag">JavaScript API</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Webhook integration</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Custom actions</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Event tracking</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">A/B testing</span>
              <span class="ux-tag">Developer tools</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Ready to Transform Your Website?</h2>
          <p>Join thousands of websites that have revolutionized their user experience with Minimal's intelligent conversational interface.</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="https://minimal.lat" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Free</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Sales</a>
          </div>
          <p class="cta-note">No credit card required ‚Ä¢ 14-day free trial ‚Ä¢ Cancel anytime</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
